Yiimp Install Scrypt v1.1 // 19.09.2020

Changes / Information =>
* 16.04 deprecated. Works with Ubuntu Server 18.04.
* Add script to remove all coins as part of menu.
* Installer modified (new supported features - some corrections with apt).
* Removed non-debug enabled installer as really not a good idea to run silent.
* Tidied up all texts like README etc.
* Added example coin (post-install) configuration steps (based on latest 0.20 BTC fork)

Fixes =>
* Add worker names to dashboard.
* Fix apt issues (brought dependancies up-to-date)

